oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Allylic oxidation in annulated bicyclo[2.2.2]octenones: Effect of conformational flexibility of the annulated rings
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: SINGH, V
VEDANTHAM, P
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: photoreaction
tricyclopentanoids
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Allylic oxidation of annulated bicyclo[2.2.2]octenones with PDC-(BuOOH)-Bu-t has been reported. While the oxidation of 10,11 gives the usual products, the compounds 1-4 afford the enones 5-8 involving migration of the double bond.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: INDIAN JOURNAL OF CHEMISTRY SECTION B-ORGANIC CHEMISTRY INCLUDING MEDICINAL CHEMISTRY, 40(11), 1144-1147
